{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"53704093ca","title":"郭炳林给夏部长的信","origin":"四川省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3e22d55a9b","index":0,"year":1959,"month":7,"day":29,"articleId":"53704093ca"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"211c2d9c7b","type":"title","text":"郭炳林给夏部长的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"71ceb19783","type":"paragraph","text":"[中共四川省委农村工作部 郭炳林]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"02a8f02de7","type":"appellation","text":"夏部长：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"f28a2d79a1","type":"paragraph","text":"送去十日棉花调查表一分，希收阅，从十日情况看早棉花落花较多，大部分棉田结桃上升，生长正常。昨日已开队长会议，决定先施早棉花，三日内施完。立秋前后施完大部棉花，把这次肥施后成本还不到去年的一半。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"380acef98a","type":"paragraph","text":"这里肿病近日又发生起来了，全耕区已发肿的有93人，其中主劳54人，副劳29人，老年13人，小孩3人。有的是下午肿，上午好些。这个耕区不算重，据县防疫站的同志谈，全县有3万余人发年肿病，在这里的医生已抽调走一些去新市平泉等地防治去了，医生谈防治办法：4两黄糖，半斤大葱，水煎服就好了。我看这与粮食问题有关，石桥每日约有二千余人排队买肥儿粉，长此下去，要到十月分才能吃红苕，还有两个月，可能出大问题的，希省领导注意简阳县的口粮问题。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"a6289ff39e","type":"paragraph","text":"我7月31日准备回去一次。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"df9c11a64a","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"290a89af61","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"f0608c0cd2","type":"paragraph","text":" 郭炳林1959年7月29日","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"4326d1bf37","type":"paragraph","text":"抄送：志高、梦侠同志，办公厅（2），卫生厅分党组。  （印8分）","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"},{"id":"33e4446563","type":"paragraph","text":"收文第5107号  中共四川省委办公厅秘书处1959年8月1日抄","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca"}],"page":{"id":"5f39880a35","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"53704093ca","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}